WEBVTT

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:07.736
Shah Rukh Khan: When we as parents, elders,
teachers, uncles and aunts ask children

00:00:07.760 --> 00:00:11.176
what they want to be when they grow up,

00:00:11.200 --> 00:00:15.016
we want to hear answers we are comfortable
with -- like doctor, engineer, MBA

00:00:15.040 --> 00:00:19.136
or maybe in some homes
actor, singer or cricketer.

00:00:19.160 --> 00:00:25.976
In a nutshell, we want
our children to be successful.

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:29.576
Yet, there is a Mumbai-based lady,
a mother of two, Supriya Joshi,

00:00:29.600 --> 00:00:33.976
whose dream for her children
was just that they grow up